longBusinessSummary: GBX International Group Inc. engages in the financing, development, and distribution of various feature films in the theatrical motion picture markets. The company was formerly known as Bridgegate Pictures Corp. GBX International Group Inc. was founded in 1997 and is based in Corona, California.
